p to time. The foundation of her practice is the transformation of surfaces. Half Japanese & half Russian-American, Ando is a descendant of Bizen sword makers and spent part of her childhood in a Buddhist temple in Japan as well as on 25 acres of redwood forest in rural coastal Northern California. She has continued her 16th-generation Japanese sword smithing and Buddhist lineage by combining metals, reflectivity and light in her luminous paintings and sculpture.\",\"Genre\":[\"Post-minimalism\",\"Color Field\"],\"Collection\":[\"recoOI0BXBdmR4JfZ\"]},\"createdTime\":\"2015-02-10T16:53:03.000Z\"},{\"id\":\"recP4Yai8DXrhFSex\",\"fields\":{\"Name\":\"Barnett Newman\",\"Attachments\":[{\"id\":\"attBuWxIL3tSjGMdF\",\"url\":\"https://dl.airtable.com/2cDrlmbJQrWGsnzfEKc5_The_Promise.jpg\",\"filename\":\"The_Promise.jpg\",\"size\":7673,\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"thumbnails\":{\"small\":{\"url\":\"https://dl.airtable.com/B79n8x4HTgO7JJpgFdTu_small_The_Promise.jpg\",\"width\":48,\"height\":36},\"large\":{\"url\":\"https://dl.airtable.com/PLvl88j6SgCvY2pP4SmU_large_The_Promise.jpg\",\"width\":512,\"height\":482},\"full\":{\"url\":\"https://dl.airtable.com/vKy9ZbqoTGazELHRamog_full_The_Promise.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":482}}},{\"id\":\"attPNPf29mbF7NF0p\",\"url\":\"https://dl.airtable.com/leePgI80QIuBojYteTJN_Newman-Who's_Afraid_of_Red%2C_Yellow_and_Blue-2.jpg\",\"filename\":\"Newman-Who's_Afraid_of_Red,_Yellow_and_Blue-2.jpg\",\"size\":4965,\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"thumbnails\":{\"small\":{\"url\":\"https://dl.airtable.com/q1Japi2KQ2GxjiF9uQxd_small_Newman-Who's_Afraid_of_Red%2C_Yellow_and_Blue-2.jpg\",\"width\":23,\"height\":36},\"large\":{\"url\":\"https://dl.airtable.com/ICWyXCFS6CLCjiat72E3_large_Newman-Who's_Afraid_of_Red%2C_Yellow_and_Blue-2.jpg\",\"width\":256,\"height\":400},\"full\":{\"url\":\"https://dl.airtable.com/I7cyvSwvRHiybrIwIvnX_full_Newman-Who's_Afraid_of_Red%2C_Yellow_and_Blue-2.jpg\",\"width\":256,\"height\":400}}},{\"id\":\"att6nWQ0EtqcIoNRB\",\"url